                                          "is_external_url":  true,
                                          "author":  "",
                                          "contents":  "\u003cimg src=\"https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/resident-evil-requiem-adult-mod-youtuber-claims-capcom-takedown-01.jpg?width=690\u0026quality=85\u0026format=jpg\u0026auto=webp\" /\u003e \u003cp\u003eA YouTuber who showcases mods which stick characters from games like \u003ca href=\"https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/games/resident-evil-9-revenant-shadows\"\u003eResident Evil Requiem\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/games/stellar-blade\"\u003eStellar Blade\u003c/a\u003e into skimpier costumes claims Capcom\u0027s legal team have sent him an email asking him to to pull over 1000 videos featuring \"adult-oriented\" mods for the publisher\u0027s games offline.\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/youtuber-who-showcases-adult-oriented-resident-evil-requiem-and-stellar-blade-mods-claims-capcoms-laywers-asked-him-to-take-down-over-1000-videos\"\u003eRead more\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e",
