                                          "url":  "https://steamstore-a.akamaihd.net/news/externalpost/steam_community_announcements/1816849002020889",
                                          "is_external_url":  true,
                                          "author":  "Wolfcastle",
                                          "contents":  "[p][img src=\"{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/45493125/b00d2ba83ae3403e8413ad76362065a4589f4772.png\"][/img][/p][p]It’s time to show your support![/p][p]Stellar Blade has captivated players around the world with its breathtaking art direction, intricate environments, and cinematic detail that brings every moment to life. Vote for Stellar Blade at the Steam Awards 2025 in the category of Outstanding Visual Style and help recognize the incredible artistry that makes it one of the most visually stunning games of the year.[/p][p][/p][p]Also, Stellar Blade is currently 20% off on Steam until Dec. 2—there’s never been a better time to experience it yourself and see why it deserves your vote![/p][p][/p][p][/p]",
